WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.040
rstudio, now Posit, is known for creating tools like rstudio and the Tidyverse, but did you know

00:00:05.040 --> 00:00:10.720
that we develop Python tools too? Libraries like GreatTables for making beautiful publication-ready

00:00:10.720 --> 00:00:17.120
tables, Shiny for Python for easy interactive apps that can scale, Chatlist for interacting

00:00:17.120 --> 00:00:22.400
with LLMs using Python, Pointblank for data validation and monitoring, and just released,

00:00:22.400 --> 00:00:27.520
GreatDocs for creating polished documentation sites. And our newer tools like Positron and

00:00:27.600 --> 00:00:31.920
Cordo are built to be natively multilingual. Are you interested in learning more about any

00:00:31.920 --> 00:00:34.240
of these tools? Let us know in the comments.

